>                                                                                      					<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product as Approved or not. Possible inputs for this field are \'Yes\' &amp; \'No\'. Default value should be set as \'Yes\' to display products in the system.</p>                                        </li>                                            				<li>                                                                                      					<h5>Active </h5>                                                                                      					<p>User defined field to mark a particular Product as active in the system or not. Possible inputs for this field are \'Yes\' &amp; \'No\'. Default value should be set as \'Yes\'. </p>                                        </li>                                            				<li>                                                                                      					<h5>Deleted </h5>                                                                                      					<p>User defined field to mark a particular product as deleted in the system or not. Possible inputs for this field are \'Yes\' &amp; \'No\'. Default value should be set as \'No\' to display products in the system. </p>                                        </li>                                        			</ul>                                </div>                            </div>                             	<div class=\"groups group-js\">                                 		<div class=\"group__head group__head-js\"> 			<h5> Seller Catalog - Product Option </h5></div>                                 		<div class=\"group__body group__body-js\">                                     			<ul>                                                                      				<li>                                                                                      					<h5>Product Identifier</h5>                                      